sequenceDiagram
    participant VMM as Userspace VMM
    participant KR as kvm_run<br/>(shared page)
    participant P0V as Plane 0 vCPU<br/>kvm_vcpu_arch
    participant P1V as Plane 1 vCPU<br/>kvm_vcpu_arch
    participant HW as CPU Hardware<br/>VMCS/VMCB

    Note over VMM,HW: === Run Plane 0 ===
    VMM->>KR: run->plane = 0
    VMM->>KR: ioctl(KVM_RUN)
    KR->>P0V: sync_regs()<br/>kvm_run.s.regs → arch regs
    P0V->>HW: VMLAUNCH/VMRESUME<br/>(plane 0 VMCS)
    HW-->>P0V: VM-Exit
    P0V->>KR: store_regs()<br/>arch regs → kvm_run.s.regs
    KR-->>VMM: exit_reason

    Note over P0V: Plane 0 register state<br/>preserved in its own<br/>kvm_vcpu_arch

    Note over VMM,HW: === Switch to Plane 1 ===
    VMM->>KR: run->plane = 1<br/>req_exit_planes = BIT(0)
    VMM->>KR: ioctl(KVM_RUN)

    Note over KR,P1V: kvm_arch_vcpu_ioctl_run()<br/>reads run->plane == 1<br/>gets plane 1 vCPU via<br/>kvm_get_plane_vcpu()

    KR->>P1V: sync_regs()<br/>kvm_run.s.regs → arch regs
    P1V->>HW: VMLAUNCH/VMRESUME<br/>(plane 1 VMCS)
    HW-->>P1V: VM-Exit

    Note over P1V: Plane 1 register state<br/>preserved in its own<br/>kvm_vcpu_arch

    P1V->>KR: store_regs()<br/>arch regs → kvm_run.s.regs
    KR-->>VMM: exit_reason

    Note over VMM,HW: === Cross-Plane Interrupt ===
    VMM->>KR: run->plane = 1<br/>req_exit_planes = BIT(0)
    VMM->>KR: ioctl(KVM_RUN)
    KR->>P1V: sync_regs()
    P1V->>HW: VMRESUME (plane 1)

    Note over P0V: IRQ arrives for plane 0<br/>irr_pending_planes |= BIT(0)<br/>KVM_REQ_PLANE_INTERRUPT

    HW-->>P1V: VM-Exit (plane interrupt)
    P1V->>KR: exit_reason = KVM_EXIT_PLANE_EVENT<br/>plane_event.target = BIT(0)
    KR-->>VMM: KVM_EXIT_PLANE_EVENT

    Note over VMM: VMM switches to plane 0<br/>to handle interrupt

    VMM->>KR: run->plane = 0
    VMM->>KR: ioctl(KVM_RUN)
    KR->>P0V: sync_regs()<br/>plane 0 regs restored
    P0V->>HW: VMRESUME (plane 0 VMCS)
